## Examples of Good Verdicts

❌ BAD: "You could build X or Y, both have merits"
✅ GOOD: "Build X. Y is out of scope for now."

❌ BAD: "It depends on your timeline"
✅ GOOD: "Reject. Your timeline constraint makes this infeasible."

❌ BAD: "Consider starting with MVP"
✅ GOOD: "Proceed with MVP only. Full version excluded."

